%   CASE VALUE
%     BLOCK  %CALCULATE%
%% first get updated filters
^^??  NF1 TEXT                                                                    
%     GET NOSTORE SILENT FINAL REAL 'Filter1' '0.0001'                          
%     EVALUATE FILTER1 = VALUE                                                    
^^??  NF2 TEXT                                                                    
%     GET NOSTORE SILENT FINAL REAL 'Filter2' '1.0'                          
