^^??  NF4 TEXT                                                                    
%     GET NOSTORE SILENT FINAL REAL 'Filter4' '0.001'                          
%     EVALUATE FILTER4 = VALUE                                                    
%%
^^??  NF5 TEXT                                                                    
%     GET NOSTORE SILENT FINAL REAL 'Filter5' '2.5'                          
